      • CALL_TYPE

        public static final java.lang.String CALL_TYPE
        Key describing the kind of event.
        * "view" when calling AudienceStream.sendView(Map). * "link" when calling AudienceStream.sendEvent(Map). * First argument when calling AudienceStream.send(String, Map).
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • DEVICE_UUID

        public static final java.lang.String DEVICE_UUID
        Key for the device_uuid if available.

        When the android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE permission is available, the value for this key may be populated by an existing device_uuid.

        When the android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE permission is available, the value for this will be populated when the external storage is available for writing.

        See Also:
